Controversial Nigerian senator, Dino Melaye has released a new song attacking the governor of Kogi state. Dino Melaye, the controversial Senator, has released a song against the incumbent Governor of Kogi State, Yahaya Bello in preparation for the November governorship election in the state. The senator’s song has caused quite a stir on Instagram. Melaye sang the song himself and it is titled” ‘Kogi Koya… Kogi ko Bello.’ Watch the video here: Kogi Koya… Kogi ko Bello A post shared by  Senator Dino Melaye (SDM) (@dinomelaye) on May 21, 2019 at 8:00am PDT Source